headline: 3 Wireless Stocks Likely to Benefit From Positive Industry Trends
summary: The accelerated pace of 5G deployment should help the Zacks Wireless National industry thrive despite short-term headwinds and raw material price volatility. TMUS, USM and ATNI are well poised to make the most of the current scenario.
